rodrigo-ornelas.content: Rodrigo is a senior at Penn studying Computer Science and Finance in the Jerome Fisher M&T Program. He has worked in algorithmic trading at Goldman Sachs London, and in software development at Microsoft. Rodrigo is interested in the role of technology in social and economic development, and he likes photography and puzzles.
